- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper deals with the synthesis of implementations from specifications, which is a topic of interest in programming languages. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper deals with decision procedures and the complexity of the realisability problem, which are related to algorithmic complexity. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possible category as the paper deals with the complexity of decision problems and the realisability problem, which are topics of interest in computational complexity theory.
